PrecisCROW BENEFIT (SOUTHERN RAILS COOPERATIVE LTD.) ORDER NO. 2 - which provides that the "Crow Benefit" payable to the aforementioned in respect of the 1994-95 to 1996-97 crop years shall be reduced by an amount equal to the amount payable under an Agreement dated July 20, 1994, between the Minister of Transport and this railroad company.
